name: 4Live Cookie
description:
This is so much more than a cookie, this is energy in a delectable treat. Filling you up in each bite is cranberries, chocolate chips, nuts, gluten-free oats, and dancing cinnamon!

Each 4 inch cookie is designed to fill you, energize you, comfort you and sustain you in each bit! Break this cookie in quarters to share or in half. Have one half for breakfast each morning or share with yourself, enjoy before your workout or after your row, run or ride!

Wholesale pricing for orders of one dozen or more!

Each cookie is 4 inches
Each order has one dozen cookies individually packaged

These delightful filling cookies are:
Gluten-Free
Vegan
Refined Sugar-Free
Soy-Free

name: Zaline Tart
description:
Let tangy and sweetness all at the same time dance around your palate as zingy lemon and sweet orange are combined into a diary free lemon orange curd! These two flavors have been poured over a gluten-free crust with layers of fresh oranges arranged on the crust. An Italian favorite!

Enjoy every bite of this experience and don't forget to share!
